        <text>\n
        * [SHIFT+dLMB], [CTRL+dLMB] and [CTRL+SHIFT+dLMB], where dLMB means double LMB click, are used to take/put more items. Check MCM for multipliers settings.\n
        * [SHIFT+F] sets focus on the search textbox.\n
        * [CTRL+SHIFT+F] sets focus on the search textbox and removes it's content.\n
        * [Enter] or unfocus search textbox to filter all items, with a respect to the selected category.\n
        * [ALT+dLMB] marks item as favorite. Repeat to remove marking. [UNIMPLEMENTED]\n
        * [SHIFT+ALT+dLMB] marks item as a trash. Repeat to remove marking. [UNIMPLEMENTED]\n
